(40, 1, 5, 6, 6, 22, 25, 'Rachab', 'Connection of Rahab and Ruth', 'Both passages emphasize the inclusion of Rahab in the lineage of significant figures in Israel. Rahab''s actions in Joshua lead to her being mentioned in Matthew as the mother of Boaz, connecting her to the ancestry of David.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
