(40, 1, 6, 9, 17, 12, 12, 'David the king begat Solomon', 'David''s Lineage and Identity', 'Both passages emphasize David''s lineage, specifically his connection to Jesse. Matthew 1:6 highlights David as a king, while 1 Samuel 17:12 identifies him as Jesse''s son, establishing his royal and familial identity.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
