(40, 1, 6, 9, 16, 1, 1, NULL, 'Connection Between David and Jesse', 'This connection highlights the lineage of David, as mentioned in both passages. Matthew 1:6 references Jesse and David, while 1 Samuel 16:1 introduces Jesse as the father of the future king, establishing a direct link between the two texts.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 6, 10, 11, 26, 27, 'the wife of Urias', 'David and Uriah''s Wife', 'Both passages emphasize David''s relationship with Uriah''s wife, highlighting the consequences of his actions. Matthew references this connection by mentioning Solomon, who was born from this union, indicating the significance of this event in the lineage of David.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 6, 10, 12, 24, 25, 'David the king begat Solomon', 'Connection Between David and Solomon', 'Both passages emphasize David''s relationship with Solomon, highlighting his lineage. Matthew 1:6 mentions David begetting Solomon, while 2 Samuel 12:24-25 describes the birth of Solomon to Bathsheba.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 6, 8, 4, 22, 22, 'Jesse begat David', 'Genealogy of David', 'Both passages emphasize the lineage of David, connecting Jesse and David directly. Matthew 1:6 references David as a king, while Ruth 4:22 traces his ancestry back to Obed and Jesse.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 6, 13, 3, 5, 5, 'David the king begat Solomon', 'David and Solomon''s Lineage', 'Both passages emphasize the lineage of David and Solomon, highlighting their familial connection. Matthew specifically mentions Solomon as the son of David, while Chronicles lists Solomon among David''s descendants.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 7, 14, 14, 1, 15, 'Asa', 'Connection of Asa''s Reign', 'Both passages emphasize Asa''s lineage and his righteous actions. Matthew 1:7 establishes Asa''s genealogy, while 2 Chronicles 14 details his reforms and victories, showcasing his faithfulness to God.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 1, 7, 11, 14, 31, 31, 'Roboam begat Abia', 'Rehoboam and Abijam Connection', 'This connection highlights the lineage of Rehoboam and his son Abijam. Both passages mention Rehoboam''s role as a father and the continuation of his line through Abijam.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
